how to understand and approah a problem...

1.identify if you can break a problem into smaller problems.
2.write the recurrence relation if needed.
3.draw the recursion tree.
4.about the tree...
     ! see the flow of function,how they are getting in stack.
     ! identify and focus of left and right tree calls.
     ! draw the tree and position again & again using paper.

5.see how the returned at each stage.